RootTable.Filter: select c.ea_guid AS CLASSGUID,c.object_type AS CLASSTYPE,c.name AS Name, c.stereotype AS Stereotype ,package.name AS PackageName ,package_p1.name AS PackageLevel1,package_p2.name AS PackageLevel2,package_p3.name AS PackageLevel3 from ((((t_object c inner join t_package package on c.package_id = package.package_id) left join t_package package_p1 on package_p1.package_id = package.parent_id) left join t_package package_p2 on package_p2.package_id = package_p1.parent_id) left join t_package package_p3 on package_p3.package_id = package_p2.parent_id) where c.ea_guid like '<Search Term>'

select o.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, o.Object_Type AS CLASSTYPE ,o.name, o.Stereotype ,package.name AS PackageName, package_p1.name AS Package_level1, package_p2.name AS Package_level2, package_p3.name AS Package_level3 from t_object o inner join t_package package on o.package_id = package.package_id left join t_package package_p1 on package_p1.package_id = package.parent_id left join t_package package_p2 on package_p2.package_id = package_p1.parent_id left join t_package package_p3 on package_p3.package_id = package_p2.parent_id where o.Stereotype in ('KPI_Measure', 'KPI_Dimension') and '{088BFFC9-449F-4c5e-B227-40C0D810D63A}' in (package.ea_guid, package_p1.ea_guid, package_p2.ea_guid, package_p3.ea_guid) and o.Name like '#WC#<Search Term>#WC#' order by o.Name

select a.ea_guid AS CLASSGUID, 'Attribute' AS CLASSTYPE, a.Name, a.Style as AttrAlias, o.Name as ClassName, o.Alias as ClassAlias, a.Type , package.name as PackageName ,package_p1.name as Package_level1,package_p2.name as Package_level2 ,package_p3.name as Package_level3 from t_attribute a inner join t_object o on o.Object_ID = a.Object_ID inner join t_package package on package.Package_ID = o.Package_ID left join t_object dt on dt.Object_ID = a.Classifier left join t_attributetag tv on tv.ElementID = a.ID and tv.Property in ('linkedAttribute', 'linkedElement', 'linkedAssociation') and tv.VALUE is not null left join t_package package_p1 on package_p1.package_id = package.parent_id left join t_package package_p2 on package_p2.package_id = package_p1.parent_id left join t_package package_p3 on package_p3.package_id = package_p2.parent_id where 1=1 and isnull(dt.Stereotype, '') <> 'XSDComplexType' and o.Package_ID in (#Branch#) and tv.ea_guid is null order by o.Name, a.pos, a.Name

Search.Name: KPI Measures and Dimensions with Status

RootTable.Filter: select o.ea_guid AS CLASSGUID, o.Object_Type AS CLASSTYPE, o.Name ,o.Stereotype ,case when o.Note like '<b>datatype:%' or o.Note like '<b>Expression%' then 'Te Documenteren' when o.Note like '?%' then 'Vraagteken' else 'Gedocumenteerd' end as Status ,p.Name as package, p2.Name as Package_p2, p3.Name as Package_p3 from t_object o inner join t_package p on p.package_ID = o.Package_ID inner join t_package p2 on p2.Package_ID = p.Parent_ID left join t_package p3 on p3.Package_ID = p2.Parent_ID where o.stereotype in ('KPI_Dimension', 'KPI_Measure') and '{088BFFC9-449F-4c5e-B227-40C0D810D63A}' in (p.ea_guid, p2.ea_guid, p3.ea_guid)

select * from (select a.ea_guid AS CLASSGUID, 'Attribute' AS CLASSTYPE, o.Name as ClassName, a.Name as Name, a.Type, tvo.Value as Owner , tvts.VALUE as Timesliced , tvav.VALUE as Availability, tvint.VALUE as Integrity, tvconf.VALUE as Confidentiality , tvacc.VALUE as Accuracy, tvcri.VALUE as Critical, tvdtk.VALUE as DataKind, tvgdpr.VALUE as GDPR, tvinte.VALUE as Intern_Extern, tvqp.VALUE as QualityPeriodicity , tvra.VALUE as RisAppetite, tvrc.VALUE as RiskClassification, tvsui.VALUE as Suitability , a.Stereotype, a.Notes as Description , package.name as PackageName ,package_p1.name as Package_level1,package_p2.name as Package_level2 ,package_p3.name as Package_level3 from t_attribute a inner join t_object o on o.Object_ID = a.Object_ID left join t_objectproperties tvo on tvo.Object_ID = o.Object_ID and tvo.Property = 'Owner' left join t_attributetag tvacc on tvacc.ElementID = a.ID and tvacc.Property = 'Accuracy' left join t_attributetag tvcri on tvcri.ElementID = a.ID and tvcri.Property = 'Critical' left join t_attributetag tvdtk on tvdtk.ElementID = a.ID and tvdtk.Property = 'DataKind' left join t_attributetag tvgdpr on tvgdpr.ElementID = a.ID and tvgdpr.Property = 'GDPR' left join t_attributetag tvinte on tvinte.ElementID = a.ID and tvinte.Property = 'Intern_Extern' left join t_attributetag tvqp on tvqp.ElementID = a.ID and tvqp.Property = 'Quality Periodicity' left join t_attributetag tvra on tvra.ElementID = a.ID and tvra.Property = 'Risk Appetite' left join t_attributetag tvrc on tvrc.ElementID = a.ID and tvrc.Property = 'Risk Classification' left join t_attributetag tvsui on tvsui.ElementID = a.ID and tvsui.Property = 'Suitability' left join t_attributetag tvav on tvav.ElementID = a.ID and tvav.Property = 'Availability' left join t_attributetag tvint on tvint.ElementID = a.ID and tvint.Property = 'Integrity' left join t_attributetag tvconf on tvconf.ElementID = a.ID and tvconf.Property = 'Confidentiality' left join t_attributetag tvts on tvts.ElementID = a.ID and tvts.Property = 'Timesliced' inner join t_package package on package.Package_ID = o.Package_ID left join t_package package_p1 on package_p1.package_id = package.parent_id left join t_package package_p2 on package_p2.package_id = package_p1.parent_id left join t_package package_p3 on package_p3.package_id = package_p2.parent_id where a.Stereotype = 'LDM_Attribute' and package.Package_ID in (#Branch#) union select o.ea_guid AS CLASSGUID, o.Object_Type AS CLASSTYPE, o.Name as ClassName, null as AttributeName, null as Type, tvo.Value as Owner , null as Timesliced , null as Availability, null as Integrity, null as Confidentiality , null as Accuracy, null as Critical, null as DataKind, null as GDPR, null as Intern_Extern, null as QualityPeriodicity , null as RisAppetite, null as RiskClassification, null as Suitability , o.Stereotype, o.Note as Description , package.name as PackageName ,package_p1.name as Package_level1,package_p2.name as Package_level2 ,package_p3.name as Package_level3 from t_object o left join t_objectproperties tvo on tvo.Object_ID = o.Object_ID and tvo.Property = 'Owner' inner join t_package package on package.Package_ID = o.Package_ID left join t_package package_p1 on package_p1.package_id = package.parent_id left join t_package package_p2 on package_p2.package_id = package_p1.parent_id left join t_package package_p3 on package_p3.package_id = package_p2.parent_id where o.Stereotype like 'LDM%' and package.Package_ID in (#Branch#) union select o.ea_guid AS CLASSGUID, c.Connector_Type AS CLASSTYPE, o.Name as ClassName, c.Name as Name, ot.Name as Type, tvo.Value as Owner , tvts.VALUE as Timesliced , null as Availability, null as Integrity, null as Confidentiality , null as Accuracy, null as Critical, null as DataKind, null as GDPR, null as Intern_Extern, null as QualityPeriodicity , null as RisAppetite, null as RiskClassification, null as Suitability , c.Stereotype, c.Notes as Description , package.name as PackageName ,package_p1.name as Package_level1,package_p2.name as Package_level2 ,package_p3.name as Package_level3 from t_connector c inner join t_object o on o.Object_ID = c.Start_Object_ID left join t_objectproperties tvo on tvo.Object_ID = o.Object_ID and tvo.Property = 'Owner' left join t_connectortag tvts on tvts.ElementID = c.Connector_ID and tvts.Property = 'Timesliced' inner join t_object ot on ot.Object_ID = c.End_Object_ID inner join t_package package on package.Package_ID = o.Package_ID left join t_package package_p1 on package_p1.package_id = package.parent_id left join t_package package_p2 on package_p2.package_id = package_p1.parent_id left join t_package package_p3 on package_p3.package_id = package_p2.parent_id where c.Stereotype like 'LDM%' and package.Package_ID in (#Branch#) ) ldm order by ClassName, CASE WHEN CLASSTYPE = 'Class' THEN 1 WHEN CLASSTYPE = 'Attribute' then 2 ELSE 3 END ,Name

on tvcri.ElementID = a.ID and tvcri.Property = 'Critical' left join t_attributetag tvdtk on tvdtk.ElementID = a.ID and tvdtk.Property = 'DataKind' left join t_attributetag tvpr on tvpr.ElementID = a.ID and tvpr.Property = 'Privacy' left join t_attributetag tvinte on tvinte.ElementID = a.ID and tvinte.Property = 'Intern_Extern' left join t_attributetag tvqp on tvqp.ElementID = a.ID and tvqp.Property = 'Quality Periodicity' left join t_attributetag tvra on tvra.ElementID = a.ID and tvra.Property = 'Risk Appetite' left join t_attributetag tvrc on tvrc.ElementID = a.ID and tvrc.Property = 'Risk Classification' left join t_attributetag tvsui on tvsui.ElementID = a.ID and tvsui.Property = 'Suitability' left join t_attributetag tvav on tvav.ElementID = a.ID and tvav.Property = 'Availability' left join t_attributetag tvint on tvint.ElementID = a.ID and tvint.Property = 'Integrity' left join t_attributetag tvconf on tvconf.ElementID = a.ID and tvconf.Property
